@startuml
title MicroMeet - Activity Diagram (Invite / Approve Participants)

start
:1. Host opens Manage Participants screen;
:2. Host selects a user and action (Invite/Approve);
:3. System validates action request;

if (Request valid?) then (Yes)
  :4. System loads meetup;
  :5. System validates target user;
  if (Action = Approve?) then (Yes)
    :6. System checks capacity;
    if (Capacity available?) then (Yes)
      :7. System updates participation status;
      :8. System saves updated roster;
      :9. System sends approval notification;
      :10. Show updated roster;
    else (No)
      :11. Show "Meetup full" error;
    endif
  else (Invite)
    :12. System creates invite entry;
    :13. System saves updated roster;
    :14. System sends invite notification;
    :15. Show updated roster;
  endif
else (No)
  :16. Show validation errors;
endif

stop

legend bottom
Steps mapping (numbers match actions):
1 Open manage participants
2 Select user + action
3 Validate request
4 Load meetup
5 Validate target user
6 Check capacity (approve)
7 Update participation status
8 Save roster
9 Send approval notification
10 Show roster
11 Meetup full error
12 Create invite entry
13 Save roster
14 Send invite notification
15 Show roster
16 Validation errors
endlegend

@enduml